snippet.title: Blue Libra 2 trailer
snippet.description:
Blue Libra 2 is a real time space strategy game.
Play single player campaign or multiplayer across many platforms. Play on iPad/iPhone/iPod as well as stationary PCs with Windows or MacOS.
Try it out at http://orator-games.com/index.php/games/blue-libra-2/
